page.title: 06HOME LIFE CLAPHAM WEEKDAY
page.content: In the morning I get up at eight o clock and get dressed and have a wash.I go down-stairs and have my breakfast for breakfast I have Muesli then Iget my coat and go to school.I walk to school.First I play and then I go down for assembly.Then I do maths after that is another play time soon after that is lunch my normal lunch is lettuce,cucumber and tomatoes.After school I go home and play lego until four o clock then I watch television to halfpast five. Then I go out until seven o clock when I come in I have supper.My favourite is chips,sausage and peas.After supper I play lego until ten p.m.Then I go upstairs and go to bed.
